These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, thriller, sports, disaster
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, blend, ritmeester, bolivar
1. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching family movies and the blend-smoker##2
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching family movies##7
4. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
6. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | disaster       | thriller | family        |
| Cigar      | ritmeester  | blend | bolivar        | tiparillo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, family, comedy, horror
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, rock, reggae, techno
1. the fan techno is somewhere between the fan reggae and the person watching comedy movies##7
2. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5
3. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the fan techno##5
4. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the fan techno is between the fan reggae and the fan rock##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Movie-Genre     | comedy | family       | horror         | action     |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | techno | reggae | dubstep |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, dahlia, daisy, sunflower
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, grapes, eggplant, plum
1. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the person eating plum is somewhere between the person eating grapes and the person eating raspberry##7
3. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person eating raspberry is somewhere between the person eating plum and the person who growsdahlia##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Flower   | dahlia | sunflower | daisy | azalea  |
| Food   | eggplant | raspberry  | plum   | grapes |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, december, november, october
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, taxi, jet-ski, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person driving the taxi and the person who's birthday is in october##7
3. the person who's birthday is in november is the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Birthday   | december | august | october       | november |
| Transport   | taxi      | helicopter   | jet-ski | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, badminton, golf, biathlon
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, ranch-style, colonial
1. the colonial house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
2. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the colonial house is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is basketball##7
5. the colonial house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
6. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Sport         | golf | basketball   | biathlon | badminton |
| House   | gothic-revival      | cape-cod | colonial      | ranch-style |

