.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, cherry, spinach, cauliflower
4 different pets are kept: fish, turtle, bird, goldfish
1. the person eating spinach is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the bird is the person eating cauliflower##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
5. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the owner of the turtle##7
7. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person eating spinach##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Food      | cherry | cranberry      | spinach | cauliflower     |
| Pet   | fish    | goldfish | turtle   | bird |

