.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, august, february, july
4 different pets are kept: bird, snake, cat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in february##7
5. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday          | july    | march   | august | february  |
| Pet   | bird | cat | guinea-pig    | snake |

