.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, taxi, ship, bus
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, chestnut, black, fuchsia
1. the person driving the taxi is not the person who likes fuchsia##6
2. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
3. the person driving the bus is the person who likes black##1
4. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the person driving the subway##7
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes black##1
7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Transport   | bus | ship | taxi | subway |
| Color           | black   | fuchsia    | pink       | chestnut  |

