.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, march, july, december
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, tea, sprite
1. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person drinking sprite##7
2. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person drinking tea##6
3. the person drinking cola is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
4. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
5. the person who's birthday is in april is the person drinking juice##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | april | december | march | july |
| Beverage           | juice    | cola   | sprite  | tea      |

