.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, cola, sprite
4 different games are played: domino, snooker, whist, go
1. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing domino##1
3. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking 7up and the person playing snooker##2
6. the person playing whist is somewhere between the person playing snooker and the person drinking 7up##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage   | sprite | coffee | 7up | cola   |
| Game   | snooker    | whist      | domino      | go |

