5. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the bolivar-smoker##5
6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
