.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-16::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, montecristo, baccarat, alhambra
City: marseilles, prague, san-francisco, new-york
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere between the montecristo-smoker and the person traveling to marseilles##7
5. the person traveling to prague is somewhere between the person traveling to san-francisco and the vegafina-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
| Cigar           | vegafina | alhambra | baccarat | montecristo  |
| City   | marseilles     | prague   | san-francisco    | new-york |

