4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
5. the nurse is on the left or right of the videographer##3
6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
| Job    | videographer   | nurse  | firefighter  | lawyer |
| Sport   | lacrosse | cycling | soccer | tennis    |

