.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
House: gothic-revival, modern, victorian, craftsman
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, thriller, comedy, epic
1. the victorian house is somewhere between the person watching sports movies and the modern house##7
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the craftsman house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
5. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| House         | modern    | victorian | craftsman     | gothic-revival |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | epic  | thriller | sports |

 